    Named ranges
        Name a range of columns or rows
        Benefits include
            Easier to reference range in formulas
            Less time searching sheets for important ranges of data
        Name Manager feature allows
            Edit named ranges
            Create new named ranges
            Deleted named ranges
    Subtotals
        Sense check numerical data through calculations
        Can help spot large anomalies early on
        Creates aggregation within the dataset
            Sum
            Count
            Average
            Grand total
    Data Validation
        Useful when sharing workbooks
        Allows user to control the values entered into a cell
            Including the data type
        Can add input messaes to inform user of data validation settings
        Customize error message if user enters invalid data
    Formatting Data
        Can format whole sheets, invidual cells, or specific values
            Font size
            Sheets with borders around all cells
            Values matching their data type (ex: currencies)
        Conditional formatting
            Allows users to set conditions for highlighting cells within data
            Helps identify patterns/trends
            Options
                Icons
                Data bars
                Highlighting cells using color scales
            Create, edit, and delete rules through Manage Rules windoew
    Custom Formats
        Many available formats for different data types
        Custom section also available

