    Select all columns
        CTRL + SHIFT + Down Key
    Name range creation
        Formulas -> Define Name -> Click okay
        Names can now be used for the whole column (or whatever range chosen) when using formulas
    Name Manager
        Formulas -> Name Manager
    Duplicate Sheet
        Right click tab -> Move or Copy -> Create a copy -> Click okay
    Subtotal
        Data -> Subtotal -> Choose whatever function and specifics necessary -> Click 2 in the top left to see
    Data Validation
        Data -> Data Validation -> Settings -> Allow criteria -> Input message (shows up if not)
    Custom Formatting
        Home -> Number Format dropdown -> More Number Formats -> Custom
    Highlighting
        Home -> Conditional Formatting -> Top/Bottom Rules -> whatever you want

