    Functions
        Preset formulas that help perform mathematical, statistical, and logical operations
    Aggregate Functions
        Summarize a group of values into a single result
            SUM()
                Total of all values in the column
            AVERAGE()
                Central or typical value in a set of numbers
                Sum of all values divided by number of records
                    AVERAGE(B2:B11)
                    AVERAGE(B:B)
                    AVERAGE(Students[Test Score])
            COUNT()
                Number of records
            MIN()
                Minimum value in the column
            MAX()
                Maximum value in the column

